I'm assuming that my connection was lost less than 30 seconds after I started my notes on a 1 hour conference call. Nothing was saved. 

I'm wondering if a warning message can pop up when the connection is lost warning the user that the information can be lost. 

It's a big disappointment that is not necessarily an issue with Confluence, but it is something Confluence may be able to improve the user experience with.

