When using the Email operation to send a page as an email, currently the user lookup field is very clumsy. This is a good field to be ajaxified.

When formatting a text using e.g. _ or ?? the formatting is not done in case the text contains special chars like » « .

{code}
The following text: _should be »printed« in italic_
{code}

It does seem to work in jira but not confluence. It does work in confluence if you format the word with the special characters seperately:

{code}
The following text: _should be_ _»printed«_ _in italic_
{code}

