Currently space pdf export allows you to choose whether or not comments are included in the export.  Page export provides no option screen, as it is a quick one-click export.  The comments are never exported by the page export.  It would be nice if they were exported when shown, and not exported when not shown.  That is, they should follow the hide comments/show comments link.

